name: Physics-simulator
body:
### Physics Simulator (PCC CS Project) This project is a collaboration between several computer science students at Pasadena City College. If you are a PCC CS student and would like to contribute, please email me the following information:
  • Name
  • Preferred contact method (email or phone number)
  • (Optional) Secondary contact method
  • (Optional)Area of interest or experience regarding the project
